  <!-- EN: AI2A -->
  <AM_AI2A.label>AI2應急藥盒</AM_AI2A.label>
  <!-- EN: Some emergency medicines packaged in a small plastic box. -->
  <AM_AI2A.description>一個裝著急救藥品的小塑料盒。</AM_AI2A.description>
  
  <!-- EN: analgesic regeneration injector -->
  <AM_AnalgesicRegenerationInjector.label>止痛型再生注射器</AM_AnalgesicRegenerationInjector.label>
  <!-- EN: An injector that stimulates the regeneration process by increasing the biosynthesis of purine and pyrimidine bases, RNA, and functional enzymes to promote cellular elements. It says there might be side effects within a few days of injection. -->
  <AM_AnalgesicRegenerationInjector.description>通過增加嘌呤和嘧啶堿基、RNA、功能性酶促細胞元素的生物合成來刺激細胞再生過程。能夠增加新陳代謝、健康和生命力。但是在注射的幾天后會產生副作用。</AM_AnalgesicRegenerationInjector.description>
  <!-- EN: Use {0_label} -->
  <AM_AnalgesicRegenerationInjector.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>使用 {0_label}</AM_AnalgesicRegenerationInjector.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>
  <!-- EN: inject {0} -->
  <AM_AnalgesicRegenerationInjector.ingestible.ingestCommandString>注射 {0} </AM_AnalgesicRegenerationInjector.ingestible.ingestCommandString>
  <!-- EN: injecting {0}. -->
  <AM_AnalgesicRegenerationInjector.ingestible.ingestReportString>注射 {0} </AM_AnalgesicRegenerationInjector.ingestible.ingestReportString>
  
  <!-- EN: ancient grizzly kit -->
  <AM_AncientGrizzly.label>遠古灰熊急救包</AM_AncientGrizzly.label>
  <!-- EN: Considered one of the best first aid kits. It contains all medical supplies one could need in extreme situations. Its packaging is dilapidated, but it seems the medicine can still be used. -->
  <AM_AncientGrizzly.description>灰熊急救包被認為是最好的急救箱之一。它包含了在極端情況下可能需要的所有醫療用品。它的包裝破舊不堪，但里面的藥物仍然可以正常使用。</AM_AncientGrizzly.description>
  
