  <!-- EN: first aid kit -->
  <AM_FirstAidKit.label>車載急救包</AM_FirstAidKit.label>
  <!-- EN: A medical kit commonly used as a backup in cars. It contains basic drugs, tools for suturing and bone setting, diagnostic devices, and various pads and fluids. -->
  <AM_FirstAidKit.description>一種通常用作汽車備用的醫療箱。它包含基本藥物、縫合和骨固定工具、診斷設備以及各種襯墊和藥劑。</AM_FirstAidKit.description>
  
  <!-- EN: grizzly kit -->
  <AM_Grizzly.label>灰熊急救包</AM_Grizzly.label>
  <!-- EN: Considered one of the best first aid kits. It contains all medical supplies one could need in extreme situations. -->
