  <!-- EN: metalblood injector -->
  <AM_MetalbloodInjector.label>鋼血注射器</AM_MetalbloodInjector.label>
  <!-- EN: A blood stimulant used in combat. It was discovered that it does not cause discoloration of the skin at a special concentration dose, which improves the ability of muscle tissue to withstand impact damage and to some extent increases movement speed. However, it is also can make its user susceptible to fire damage and hightens their metabolism. -->
  <AM_MetalbloodInjector.description>在戰斗中使用的鋼血興奮劑，它在特定濃度劑量下不會導致皮膚變色，提高了肌肉組織承受沖擊損傷的能力，并在一定程度上提高了運動速度。然而，它也使注射者更容易受到火焰傷害，新陳代謝也變得更高。</AM_MetalbloodInjector.description>
